      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:26:15",
      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " سَمِعْتُهُ يَقُولُ كَانَ عَلِيٌّ ( عليه السلام ) يَقُولُ إِذَا قَالَ الرَّجُلُ لِلرَّجُلِ يَا مَعْفُوجَ وَ يَا مَنْكُوحَ فِي دُبُرِهِ فَإِنَّ عَلَيْهِ الْحَدَّ حَدَّ الْقَاذِفِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ibn Mahboub, from Abbad Bin Suheyb, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup>, (the narrator says), ‘I heard him<sup>asws</sup> saying: ‘Ali<sup>asws</sup> was saying: ‘When the man says to the man, ‘O passive sodomist!’, and ‘O one copulated with in his backside!’, so upon him is the Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>), a Penalty (<span class=\"iTxt\">Hadd</span>) of the slanderer’."
        ]
      }
    }
